This is simple implementation of BLE sniffer based on nRF51 Dongle hardware. More information is avaiable on https://www.nordicsemi.com/eng/Products/Bluetooth-low-energy/nRF-Sniffer.
Sniffer software was written using Qt libraries.

Usage: ./nrf-sniffer [options] COM_PORT
BLE sniffer

Options:
  --list                    List all serial devices and exit
  --air-quality             Enable air quality monitor
  --silent                  Don't report ble packets
  --ch-list <channel_mask>  Comma separated scan channels
                            Default: 37,38,39
  -h, --help                Displays this help.

Arguments:
  Device port               COM port for serial device.
